# URL of the AppBase API (no trailing slash). Server-side only — read at process start, not baked into `next build`.
# Local: copy to `.env`. Docker/Compose: pass with `-e API_BASE_URL=...` or `environment:` / `env_file:` (do not COPY `.env` into the image).
# Default API dev port is often 3000; the all-in-one Docker image uses API on 8000 (see appbase.env.example).
API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:3000

# Optional: first-operator bootstrap in production (must match API APPBASE_BOOTSTRAP_SECRET)
# APPBASE_BOOTSTRAP_SECRET=
# DASHBOARD_BOOTSTRAP_SECRET=
